title: VideoGameDunkey Parody - Monkey Madness

embed.description: This chimp got some bark to that bite. Go to https://youtube.com/videogamedunkey for more like this!

body:
A small parody of VideoGameDunkey. I plan on doing other parody videos both of Dunkey and other Youtubers i.e. Jontron, CaptainSparkles, etc.

Please leave your feedback, subscribe if you wish, and I want to thank you guys for looking at it. Enjoy!

Crono
{{champion:62}}

replies.body: Exactly, just a parody/abridged thing. If you watch VideoGameDunkey you'd get it

CaptainSparkles?
Who the fuck is that??
